    "data": [
        [
            [
                "Dialogue"
            ],
            [
                "The classes are over, and I rush my way to the exit."
            ],
            [
                "What could be that thing [he] said I'll like?"
            ],
            [
                "A metallic scratch is heard near me, making me turn over."
            ],
            [
                "[tn]!!"
            ],
            [
                "Helpie? What happened?"
            ],
            [
                "I 4Can't he1p mysel4f!"
            ],
            [
                "ERROR UDECLARED STR-"
            ],
            [
                "//ERR [tn]! H2lp me, I got into a [KERFUFFLE] of d1sgraceful [CONSEQUENCES]."
            ],
            [
                "What? What did you do?"
            ],
            [
                "I tried to tell you [HIGH PRORITY] n0tice!"
            ],
            [
                "Until a (high_speed)Vehicle. Ram through me!"
            ],
            [
                "You crossed the streets and dragged yourself all the way here?!"
            ],
            [
                "It was worth it! to tell [MAIN USER] that... ERR---"
            ],
            [
                "We need to get you to a repair shop or something."
            ],
            [
                "APRECIATION VARIABLE =+1;"
            ],
            [
                "I rush in into the closest repair shop I find, Though the adverts are for phones not androids."
            ],
            [
                "Hi, Uh, I need help, my friend... It got ran over by a car. I need fixing asap!"
            ],
            [
                "Uhm, yeah... Well I dunno."
            ],
            [
                "Things very damaged, id' say you buy another one."
            ],
            [
                "Helpies face changes into a printed >:( for brief moments"
            ],
            [
                "Come on, you gotta do something, I don't want Helpie to shut off or something."
            ],
            [
                "Alright... Uhum.. It's gonna be some time to get em fixed. But I think I can save some of it."
            ],
            [
                "Time passes."
            ],
            [
                "Alright, here's yo bot. All runing, well. the little it can."
            ],
            [
                "Helpie are you alright?"
            ],
            [
                "[UNEXPECTED ERROR PURGING ALL DATA]"
            ],
            [
                "WHAT? NO!"
            ],
            [
                "Helpie's face just changes into a pixel form of a smily face."
            ],
            [
                "Don't worry, just messing."
            ],
            [
                "HEY! Not cool!"
            ],
            [
                "Whatever, what even was the very important thing you wanted to tell me?"
            ],
            [
                "Important enought to get hit by a car."
            ],
            [
                "Oh, yes, [tn] I got two tickets for something very special."
            ],
            [
                "SOMETHING VERY SPECIAL? THE BAND?"
            ],
            [
                "Yeah at the late autumn music festival."
            ],
            [
                "Oh my god, how did you got them? They are crazy requested!"
            ],
            [
                "Waited 16 hours in the virtual queue. But I know it's been a dream you had."
            ],
            [
                "The phone buzzes."
            ],
            [
                "17 messages from Victor"
            ],
            [
                "Oh, I screwed up didn't I?"
            ],
            [
                "Hey are you really coming by?"
            ],
            [
                "YES, Yes, I'm already on my way! Sorry!"
            ],
            [
                "Meet me at my apartment."
            ],
            [
                "I reach Victor's apartment complex."
            ],
            [
                "I stand akwardly outside, and see [his] head pop out of the balcony. And backs out."
            ],
            [
                "A makeshift of mutliple cords begins decending from the balcony holding something attached."
            ],
            [
                "The cords reach me and I see a note attached to it and separate it."
            ],
            [
                "It reads \"Follow behind the building for a treat\""
            ],
            [
                "You have reached the end. remember this is a work in progress."
            ],
